This document contains learning objectives and practice exercises for each SOP.

How to Use This Training Manual
This manual teaches you to operate the FNF Agent Stack from scratch. Each SOP (Standard Operating Procedure) follows the same structure:

Section
Purpose
Learning Objectives
What you will know and be able to do after completing this SOP
Overview Table
Quick reference — purpose, prerequisites, expected output, time
Steps
The procedure itself — follow in order, do not skip steps
Practice Exercise
A hands-on scenario to practise what you just learned
Knowledge Check
Questions to confirm understanding before moving on


Recommended Learning Path
Complete SOPs in order on your first pass through the manual. Once familiar, use individual SOPs as reference for specific tasks.

