SOP-007  |  Running the Full Pipeline
LEARNING OBJECTIVES
By the end of this SOP you will be able to:
Run all three agents in sequence using a single command
Monitor the pipeline output across all three agent stages
Verify outputs at each stage: research brief, calendar update, WordPress draft
Describe the full content production flow from topic to published post


Purpose
Run all three agents in sequence — research, content calendar, WordPress
Prerequisites
All three agents configured, Google Sheets credentials set up for Agent 2
Time required
10-15 minutes end to end


Steps
Open terminal using SOP-001
Run the full pipeline with your topic:

python run_agents.py --all --topic "your topic here"

Watch the three stages run in sequence — Research > Content Calendar > WordPress
After completion, verify all three outputs:
   output/ folder contains a new research brief
   Google Sheet calendar has new topic suggestions
   WordPress Admin > Posts > All Posts has a new draft
Review the draft using the Brand Voice Checklist (SOP-004)
Publish when ready using SOP-004 or SOP-005

